  "stemHtml": "<p>Refer to figures or Stuttgart approach charts 11-1, 11-1A, 11-2, 11-2A from Jeppesen GSPRM 2017. <br>An aircraft departed from Stuttgart airport on Runway 07, but due to a passenger's serious illness, the pilot decided to turn back and land at Stuttgart airport following the ILS CAT III Rwy 07 approach procedure. Which approach chart should the pilot use?</p>",
  "options": {
    "a": "<p>11-1</p>",
    "b": "<p>11-1A</p>",
    "c": "<p>11-2</p>",
    "d": "<p>11-2A</p>"
  },
  "correctOption": "b",
